All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AddCommand
The AddCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that adds an element to the MyLinkedList object.
AddIfMaxCommand
The AddIfMaxCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that adds an element to the MyLinkedList object if it is greater than the current maximum element.
AddIfMinCommand
The AddIfMinCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that adds an element to the MyLinkedList object if it is less than the current minimum element.
Argument
Represents an argument for a command in the application.
AstartesCategory
The AstartesCategory enum represents the various categories of Astartes.
Chapter
The Chapter class represents a chapter in the Space Marine universe.
ClearCommand
The ClearCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that clears the MyLinkedList object.
Command
The Command class is an abstract class that defines a command that can be executed on a MyLinkedList object.
Coordinates
The Coordinates class represents a pair of coordinates.
ExecuteScriptCommand
The ExecuteScriptCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that executes a script file.
ExitCommand
The ExitCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that terminates the JVM.
HelpCommand
The HelpCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that prints a list of available commands and their descriptions.
IdComparator
A custom implementation of the Comparator interface that compares two SpaceMarine objects based on their ID field.
InfoCommand
The InfoCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that prints information about the collection.
Invoker
Invoker class that executes commands.

The main class of the program.

MyLinkedList
The MyLinkedList class represents a linked list of SpaceMarine objects.
MyLinkedListComponent
The MyLinkedListComponent interface defines a Dagger component for creating a singleton instance of the MyLinkedList class.
MyLinkedListModule
The MyLinkedListModule class defines a Dagger module for providing dependencies for the MyLinkedList class.
PrintFieldDescendingCategoryCommand
The PrintFieldDescendingCategoryCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that prints the values of the category field of each element in the collection in descending order.
PrintFieldDescendingMeleeWeaponCommand
The PrintFieldDescendingMeleeWeaponCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that prints the values of the meleeWeapon field of each element in the collection in descending order.
PrintUniqueHealthCommand
The PrintUniqueHealthCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that prints the unique values of the health field of each element in the collection.
Product
The Product class represents a product with a result and a success value.
RemoveByIdCommand
The RemoveByIdCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that removes an element from the collection by its ID.
RemoveLowerCommand
The RemoveLowerCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that removes all elements less than a given element from the collection.
SaveCommand
The SaveCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that saves the collection to a file.

ShowCommand

The SpaceMarine class represents a Space Marine.

The UpdateByIdCommand class is a concrete implementation of the Command class that updates an element in the collection by its ID.
